<% content_for(:title) { "About Us" } %>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12">
  <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-8">About Noralooks</h1>

  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-stone-200 p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-8">
    <!-- Our Story -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-4">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">Noralooks was founded with a simple belief: that every piece of jewellery should tell a story. Our passion for creating exquisite, timeless pieces comes from a deep appreciation for craftsmanship and the precious moments that jewellery commemorates.</p>
      <p class="text-stone-600">For over a decade, we've been crafting fine jewellery that celebrates life's most important moments. From everyday elegance to special occasions, each piece is designed to be cherished for generations.</p>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-stone-200">

    <!-- Our Values -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-6">What We Stand For</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex-shrink-0 bg-rose-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-rose-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Quality Craftsmanship</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Every piece is meticulously handcrafted by skilled artisans using the finest materials and traditional techniques.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex-shrink-0 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Certified Gold</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">All our gold jewellery is 100% BIS hallmarked, ensuring authenticity and purity you can trust.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex-shrink-0 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Fair Pricing</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">We believe in transparent pricing with no hidden costs. Quality jewellery at honest prices.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex-shrink-0 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Customer Care</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Your satisfaction is our priority. We're here to help at every step of your jewellery journey.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-stone-200">

    <!-- Our Commitment -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-4">Our Commitment</h2>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-50 to-amber-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">We're committed to sustainable and ethical practices in everything we do:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-700 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Responsibly sourced materials
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-700 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Support for local artisans and craftspeople
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-700 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Eco-friendly packaging and practices
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-700 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Fair labor practices throughout our supply chain
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-stone-200">

    <!-- Contact -->
    <section class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 mb-6">Have questions or want to learn more about Noralooks? We'd love to hear from you.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <%= link_to 'Contact Us', support_tickets_path, class: 'inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-rose-800 hover:bg-rose-900 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition' %>
        <%= link_to 'Shop Now', products_path, class: 'inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-stone-100 hover:bg-stone-200 text-stone-900 font-medium rounded-lg transition' %>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
